              </span><br />
              <span class="tag is-info">CSV</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="title is-5 is-marginless">Full Locations Table</h3>
              <p>
                All the data from the Locations table unfiltered.
                <em>Includes deleted records that have not been fully purged.</em>
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

